it explores how APIs facilitate seamless integration of AI to enhance application functionalities, while blockchain technology underpins these advancements with robust security features, ensuring data integrity and trust. Through industry-specific use cases, the presentation illuminates the transformative potential across finance, healthcare, and supply chain management, addressing challenges such as complexity, data privacy, and interoperability, and concluding with best practices for a successful integration. This discourse aims to provide a comprehensive overview for developers and businesses on leveraging these technologies to forge innovative, future-ready solutions.
